<h1>ʕ ᓀ ᴥ ᓂ ʔ  ~ Welcome to Burger Planet! ~ (V●ᴥ●V)</h1>

<img src="\assets\img\burger.jpg">

<h2>╰། ❛ ڡ ❛ །╯ Current Menu!</h2>

<ul>
  {{#each burgers}}
    {{#unless devoured}}
      {{> burgers/burger-block devoured=false}}
    {{/unless}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Sold Out, Sorry! (ू˃̣̣̣̣̣̣︿˂̣̣̣̣̣̣ ू) </h2>

<ul>
  {{#each burgers}}
    {{#if devoured}}
      {{> burgers/burger-block devoured=true}}
    {{/if}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>(つ•̀ᴥ•́)つ*:･ﾟ✧  Create Your Own Burger!</h2>
<form class="create-form">

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="brg">Burger Name:</label>
    <input type="text" id="brg" name="name">
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="devo">Order it now?</label><br>
    <input type="radio" name="order" value="1" checked> Order up!<br>
    <input type="radio" name="order" value="0"> I'm still thinking
  </div>

  <button type="submit">Add Burger</button>
</form>
